modName: Dovahkiin Imperial Back Tattoo for CBBE
summary: Adds my Dovahkiin logo as a large back tat on female models using CBBE.
descriptionHtml:
This tat mod requires you have Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition -CBBE- by Caliente (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666) installed first.

Adds my Dovahkiin logo as a large back tat on female models using CBBE.  Has a very realistic skin texture to it similar to real tattoo textures.  Simply extract and copy/cut and past the texture into skyrim/data/textures/actors/character/female.
author: FXtreme
